I just spoke to my machine shop and he said all the vw bushings he sees now
have seams, and the ones in my rods did as well, my mistake. The solid
bushes are not available or marginally available. He also noted that the
aluminum color of the babitted metal disappears as soon as the bushing is
honed, revealing the bronze below.

